    "client_msg_id": "346c9784-6e78-481e-b545-8ae28da6b3f6",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "My answer is \"no book\", if you'll accept that. I've never found a single resource that has given me a substantial vision of what the future of coding should be like (apart from perhaps Bret Victor's stuff). As far as I'm aware, my current vision is a collage of tiny extracts from hundreds of resources.\n\nThat probably isn't helpful :sweat_smile:.\n\nI think we should write the book we'd like to have read by now.",
